text: Trevor George McMahon (born 8 November 1929) in Wellington) is a New Zealand former cricketer. He played 5 tests for New Zealand in the 1955/56 season. He played for Wellington in the Plunket Shield. ==Other websites== * {https://www.espncricinfo.com/player/trevor-mcmahon-37710} from Cricinfo * Category:1929 births Category:Living people Category:New Zealand cricketers Category:Sportspeople from Wellington
